				<div id="contentSub">‚Üê <a href="/Authoritative_Networked_Character_Movement" title="Authoritative Networked Character Movement">Authoritative Networked Character Movement</a></div>
																<div id="mw-content-text"><p>You do not have permission to edit this page, for the following reason:
